Release Information

Skeleton Premium provides an encyclopedic reference
of skeletal anatomy that is more complete than any
other skeletal system app. It is the only app that
provides real 3D models of each bone in the
articulated skeleton, hundreds of ligaments, bone
landmarks, and moving synovial joints
